<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.5.7">
<l>nīrmaiyi ṉūṟṟuvar vīya vaivark karuḷceytu niṉṟu</l>
<l>pārmalku cēṉai yavitta parañcuṭa rainiṉain tāṭi</l>
<l>nīrmalku kaṇṇiṉa rāki neñcaṅ kuḻaintu naiyātē</l>
<l>yūṉmalki mōṭu paruppā ruttamar kaṭkeṉ ceyvārē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those whose bellies become large, abounding in flesh,</l>
<l>without dancing, thinking of the highest glow who put an end to the army abounding on earth,</l>
<l>standing while gracing the Five so that the conductless Hundred were destroyed,</l>
<l>without that water abounds in their eyes, without melting [and] languishing in the heart,</l>
	<l>what [good] will they do to the highest ones?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
